Opportunities in the Market
•	Rise in Electric and Hybrid Commercial Vehicles: While electric vehicles pose a challenge, the need for specialized lubricants in hybrid engines presents new market opportunities.
•	Increasing Demand in Emerging Markets: Rapid industrialization in Asia-Pacific, Latin America, and Africa offers lucrative growth prospects.
•	Product Innovation & Sustainability Initiatives: Market players are focusing on bio-based and low-emission lubricants to meet evolving regulatory standards and consumer preferences.

